Package org.grobid.trainer.sax

Class Summary
ChemicalClassNamesSaxParser This SAX parser simply records the chemical class name stand off annotations and their corresponding word identifiers.
ChemicalFormulasSaxParser This SAX parser simply records the chemical formula stand off annotations and their corresponding word identifiers.
ChemicalLigandSaxParser This SAX parser simply records the chemical class name stand off annotations and their corresponding word identifiers.
ChemicalNameSaxParser This SAX parser simply records the chemical name stand off annotations and their corresponding word identifiers.
ChemicalSubstancesSaxParser This SAX parser simply records the chemical substance name stand off annotations and their corresponding word identifiers.
ChemicalWordsSaxParser This SAX parser process the list of words of a document and produce the labeled data based on stand off annotations.
MPDL_METS_SaxParser SAX parser for the MPDL METS catalogue data.
NLMSaxParser SAX parser for the NLM XML format - the PubMed XML full text format.
SearchReportSaxParser SAX parser for the search report information of a patent document.
TEIAffiliationAddressSaxParser SAX parser for affiliation+address sequences encoded in the TEI format data.
TEIAuthorSaxParser SAX parser for author sequences encoded in the TEI format data.
TEICitationSaxParser SAX parser for the XML format for citation data.
TEIDateSaxParser SAX parser for author sequences encoded in the TEI format data.
TEIEbookSaxParser SAX parser for the TEI format for fulltext data.
TEIFieldExtractSaxParser Utility SAX parser which extracts all the text content under a given tag name.
TEIFulltextSaxParser SAX parser for the TEI format for fulltext data.
TEIHeaderSaxParser SAX parser for the TEI format header data.
TEIHeaderSaxParserOCRTraining SAX parser for the TEI format header data.
WikiTextExtractSaxParser SAX parser for XML Wikipedia page articles (file .hgw.xml).
